PYLOG CHEATSHEET


Logical Rules
=============

AndElimL(formulanumber)

AndElimR(formulanumber)

AndInt(formulanumber, formulanumber)

ForallElim(formulanumber, newvariable)

ForallInt(formulanumber, variable, newboundvariable)

EqualitySub(formulanumber, formulanumber, termplaceslist)

FreeSub(variablename, variablename) - shortcut for ForallInt and ForallElim where newboundvariabe is generated automatically

EquivExp(formulanumber)


Class Rules
===========

ClassElim(formulanumber)


