Input and default "pretty" display
===================================

union(x,y)               (x ∪ y)
intersection(x,y)        (x ∩ y)
extension x. A           {x: A}
forall x. A              ∀x. A
exists x. A              ∃x. A
Elem(x,y)               (x ε y)
app(f,x)                 (f'x)
pair(x,y)                {x,y}
singleton(x)             {x}
orderedpair(x,y)         (x,y)
prod(x,y)                (x X y)



